<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <div class="jumbotron">
      <h1 class="text-xs-center">
        Climate change is real.<br/>
        We are all part of the problem.</br>
        What will <strong>you</strong> do in 2016?
      </h1>

          <hr class="m-y-2">

      <p>Climate scientists say we have to reduce our greenhouse gas emissions to zero within this century. Current global greenhouse gas emissions total 45,000 million tons per year. With annual emissions of 20 metric tons of greenhouse gases per capita, we Americans are responsible for a significant portion of these emisisons.<br/><br/>

      We do not accept that this is the end of the story. That is why we are working to move Naropa University to the forefront of the global movement towards carbon neutrality. And it all starts with every single one of us. That is why we are committing to take personal action on reducing our carbon footprint &mdash; and we are inviting you to do the same.</p>

      <hr class="m-y-2">

      <h3 class="text-xs-center">But enough talking. Let's get to action.</h3>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
          <%= link_to '/signup', class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block" do %>
            <%= fa_icon "check", :class => "fa-fw" %> Let's Go
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>